{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_015beDnktq99cfCUKFhPYrkq","type":"tool_result","content":"     1â†’# Implementation History â€” 004-shared-infrastructure\n     2â†’\n     3â†’Iteration log for the autonomous spec loop. Each entry records what was\n     4â†’attempted and whether it succeeded. The agent reads this file at the start\n     5â†’of every iteration to understand prior context.\n     6â†’\n     7â†’---\n     8â†’\n     9â†’## Iteration 1 â€” lifecycle.rs\n    10â†’\n    11â†’Created `solana/shared/src/lifecycle.rs` with:\n    12â†’- `RoundPhase` enum (6 variants) with Anchor serialization derives\n    13â†’- `transition(current, target) -> Result<()>` validating 9 allowed transitions, rejecting all others\n    14â†’- `RoundTimestamps` struct with `created_at`, `locked_at`, `resolve_deadline`, `settled_at`\n    15â†’- `LifecycleError::InvalidTransition` error code\n    16â†’- 3 unit tests: valid transitions, invalid transitions (including LOCKEDâ†’SETTLED), enum serialization roundtrip\n    17â†’\n    18â†’Updated `lib.rs` to re-export `lifecycle` module.\n    19â†’\n    20â†’**Verification**: `cargo test -p rng-shared` â€” 7 tests passed (4 existing + 3 new).\n    21â†’\n    22â†’## Iteration 1 â€” 2026-02-25T21:35:21Z â€” OK\n    23â†’- **Log**: iteration-001.log\n    24â†’\n    25â†’## Iteration 2 â€” timeout.rs\n    26â†’\n    27â†’Created `solana/shared/src/timeout.rs` with:\n    28â†’- `DEFAULT_RESOLVE_TIMEOUT_SECONDS: i64 = 120` constant\n    29â†’- `TimeoutError::ResolveDeadlineExceeded` error code\n    30â†’- `is_expired(resolve_deadline, now) -> bool` â€” returns true when `now >= resolve_deadline`\n    31â†’- `enforce_not_expired(resolve_deadline, now) -> Result<()>` â€” returns error if expired\n    32â†’- 6 unit tests: boundary conditions (exactly at deadline, 1 second before, 1 second after) for both functions\n    33â†’\n    34â†’Updated `lib.rs` to re-export `timeout` module. Existing `LOCK_TIMEOUT_SECONDS` in `constants.rs` preserved.\n    35â†’\n    36â†’**Verification**: `cargo test -p rng-shared` â€” 13 tests passed (7 existing + 6 new).\n    37â†’\n    38â†’## Iteration 2 â€” 2026-02-25T21:37:45Z â€” OK\n    39â†’- **Log**: iteration-002.log\n    40â†’\n    41â†’## Iteration 3 â€” commit_reveal.rs\n    42â†’\n    43â†’Created `solana/shared/src/commit_reveal.rs` with:\n    44â†’- `CommitRevealError::CommitmentMismatch` error code\n    45â†’- `store_commitment(commitment: &mut [u8; 32], hash: [u8; 32])` â€” writes hash to storage\n    46â†’- `verify_reveal(commitment: &[u8; 32], server_seed: &[u8]) -> Result<()>` â€” computes SHA256 via `solana_sha256_hasher::hashv` and compares with stored commitment\n    47â†’- 3 unit tests: known SHA256 pair passes, tampered seed fails, empty seed fails\n    48â†’\n    49â†’Added `solana-sha256-hasher = \"2.3\"` to workspace deps and shared crate Cargo.toml (Solana SDK v2.x splits `solana_program` into subcrates â€” `hash` module now in `solana-sha256-hasher`).\n    50â†’\n    51â†’Updated `lib.rs` to re-export `commit_reveal` module.\n    52â†’\n    53â†’**Verification**: `cargo test -p rng-shared` â€” 16 tests passed (13 existing + 3 new).\n    54â†’\n    55â†’## Iteration 3 â€” 2026-02-25 â€” OK\n    56â†’\n    57â†’## Iteration 3 â€” 2026-02-25T21:45:53Z â€” OK\n    58â†’- **Log**: iteration-003.log\n    59â†’\n    60â†’## Iteration 4 â€” fees.rs update\n    61â†’\n    62â†’Updated `solana/shared/src/fees.rs` with:\n    63â†’- `MAX_FEE_BPS: u16 = 1000` compile-time safety cap\n    64â†’- Compile-time assertion: `const _: () = assert!(TOTAL_FEE_BPS <= MAX_FEE_BPS)`\n    65â†’- `calculate_net_payout(pool: u64) -> (u64, u64)` returning `(fee, net_payout)` where `net_payout = pool - fee`\n    66â†’- 2 new tests: `test_calculate_net_payout` (standard amount, zero, small rounding, 1 lamport edge case), `test_max_fee_bps_cap`\n    67â†’\n    68â†’All existing functions and tests unchanged. `fees` module already re-exported from `lib.rs`.\n    69â†’\n    70â†’**Verification**: `cargo test -p rng-shared` â€” 18 tests passed (16 existing + 2 new).\n    71â†’\n    72â†’## Iteration 4 â€” 2026-02-25T21:47:24Z â€” OK\n    73â†’- **Log**: iteration-004.log\n    74â†’\n    75â†’## Iteration 5 â€” pause.rs\n    76â†’\n    77â†’Created `solana/shared/src/pause.rs` with:\n    78â†’- `PauseError::PlatformPaused` and `PauseError::GamePaused` error codes\n    79â†’- `check_not_paused(global_paused: bool, game_paused: bool) -> Result<()>` â€” global pause takes precedence\n    80â†’- 4 unit tests: both unpaused â†’ Ok, global paused â†’ PlatformPaused, game paused â†’ GamePaused, both paused â†’ PlatformPaused (precedence)\n    81â†’\n    82â†’Updated `lib.rs` to re-export `pause` module.\n    83â†’\n    84â†’**Verification**: `cargo test -p rng-shared` â€” 22 tests passed (18 existing + 4 new).\n    85â†’\n    86â†’## Iteration 5 â€” 2026-02-25T21:49:13Z â€” OK\n    87â†’- **Log**: iteration-005.log\n    88â†’\n    89â†’"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3ef31b5a-f057-490b-97be-2b7d8a2c562f","uuid":"e3534c62-042b-41f0-82f4-3b202df3a443","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/004-shared-infrastructure/history.md","content":"# Implementation History â€” 004-shared-infrastructure\n\nIteration log for the autonomous spec loop. Each entry records what was\nattempted and whether it succeeded. The agent reads this file at the start\nof every iteration to understand prior context.\n\n---\n\n## Iteration 1 â€” lifecycle.rs\n\nCreated `solana/shared/src/lifecycle.rs` with:\n- `RoundPhase` enum (6 variants) with Anchor serialization derives\n- `transition(current, target) -> Result<()>` validating 9 allowed transitions, rejecting all others\n- `RoundTimestamps` struct with `created_at`, `locked_at`, `resolve_deadline`, `settled_at`\n- `LifecycleError::InvalidTransition` error code\n- 3 unit tests: valid transitions, invalid transitions (including LOCKEDâ†’SETTLED), enum serialization roundtrip\n\nUpdated `lib.rs` to re-export `lifecycle` module.\n\n**Verification**: `cargo test -p rng-shared` â€” 7 tests passed (4 existing + 3 new).\n\n## Iteration 1 â€” 2026-02-25T21:35:21Z â€” OK\n- **Log**: iteration-001.log\n\n## Iteration 2 â€” timeout.rs\n\nCreated `solana/shared/src/timeout.rs` with:\n- `DEFAULT_RESOLVE_TIMEOUT_SECONDS: i64 = 120` constant\n- `TimeoutError::ResolveDeadlineExceeded` error code\n- `is_expired(resolve_deadline, now) -> bool` â€” returns true when `now >= resolve_deadline`\n- `enforce_not_expired(resolve_deadline, now) -> Result<()>` â€” returns error if expired\n- 6 unit tests: boundary conditions (exactly at deadline, 1 second before, 1 second after) for both functions\n\nUpdated `lib.rs` to re-export `timeout` module. Existing `LOCK_TIMEOUT_SECONDS` in `constants.rs` preserved.\n\n**Verification**: `cargo test -p rng-shared` â€” 13 tests passed (7 existing + 6 new).\n\n## Iteration 2 â€” 2026-02-25T21:37:45Z â€” OK\n- **Log**: iteration-002.log\n\n## Iteration 3 â€” commit_reveal.rs\n\nCreated `solana/shared/src/commit_reveal.rs` with:\n- `CommitRevealError::CommitmentMismatch` error code\n- `store_commitment(commitment: &mut [u8; 32], hash: [u8; 32])` â€” writes hash to storage\n- `verify_reveal(commitment: &[u8; 32], server_seed: &[u8]) -> Result<()>` â€” computes SHA256 via `solana_sha256_hasher::hashv` and compares with stored commitment\n- 3 unit tests: known SHA256 pair passes, tampered seed fails, empty seed fails\n\nAdded `solana-sha256-hasher = \"2.3\"` to workspace deps and shared crate Cargo.toml (Solana SDK v2.x splits `solana_program` into subcrates â€” `hash` module now in `solana-sha256-hasher`).\n\nUpdated `lib.rs` to re-export `commit_reveal` module.\n\n**Verification**: `cargo test -p rng-shared` â€” 16 tests passed (13 existing + 3 new).\n\n## Iteration 3 â€” 2026-02-25 â€” OK\n\n## Iteration 3 â€” 2026-02-25T21:45:53Z â€” OK\n- **Log**: iteration-003.log\n\n## Iteration 4 â€” fees.rs update\n\nUpdated `solana/shared/src/fees.rs` with:\n- `MAX_FEE_BPS: u16 = 1000` compile-time safety cap\n- Compile-time assertion: `const _: () = assert!(TOTAL_FEE_BPS <= MAX_FEE_BPS)`\n- `calculate_net_payout(pool: u64) -> (u64, u64)` returning `(fee, net_payout)` where `net_payout = pool - fee`\n- 2 new tests: `test_calculate_net_payout` (standard amount, zero, small rounding, 1 lamport edge case), `test_max_fee_bps_cap`\n\nAll existing functions and tests unchanged. `fees` module already re-exported from `lib.rs`.\n\n**Verification**: `cargo test -p rng-shared` â€” 18 tests passed (16 existing + 2 new).\n\n## Iteration 4 â€” 2026-02-25T21:47:24Z â€” OK\n- **Log**: iteration-004.log\n\n## Iteration 5 â€” pause.rs\n\nCreated `solana/shared/src/pause.rs` with:\n- `PauseError::PlatformPaused` and `PauseError::GamePaused` error codes\n- `check_not_paused(global_paused: bool, game_paused: bool) -> Result<()>` â€” global pause takes precedence\n- 4 unit tests: both unpaused â†’ Ok, global paused â†’ PlatformPaused, game paused â†’ GamePaused, both paused â†’ PlatformPaused (precedence)\n\nUpdated `lib.rs` to re-export `pause` module.\n\n**Verification**: `cargo test -p rng-shared` â€” 22 tests passed (18 existing + 4 new).\n\n## Iteration 5 â€” 2026-02-25T21:49:13Z â€” OK\n- **Log**: iteration-005.log\n\n","numLines":89,"startLine":1,"totalLines":89}}}
